data.description: Great home in a sought after neighborhood. Offers 3 living areas, open floor plan, very large pantry. Kitchen cabinets have been upgraded, include soft close doors. Tile flooring downstairs and carpet upstairs. Take the gathering outside to the oversized covered patio. Enjoy the huge owners suite with big walk-in closet and attached bathroom with double vanities and garden tub. Make the game room a "cave" to watch the big game, movies or play pool.  Close to shopping to include IKEA; a short drive to Randolph AFB and Joint Base Ft. Sam Houston; entertaining to include Retama Park and downtown San Antonio.
